description: Unexplainable is a podcast with 2 teenage girls that have no clue what they’re doing. The podcast hosts, Dina Flamez and Hailey McFarlane, will talk you through their journey of thoughts. Each episode will bring you a new story, so keep updated!

items.content: This episode of The Unexplainable Podcast is featuring Hailey McFarlane and Dina Flamez on an adventure on the Roblox game ‘Dragon Adventures’. This episode of Unexplainable features the topics on Roblox, fights, scams, and more!
